title: Toots Thielemans - For My Lady (Dutch Treat ^B058 HQ VBR )
description:
And now something completely different. Caught by the song "Dat mistige rooie beest" (misty Red Beast) I simply had to make a special for Toots.

It is not easy to keep the tension in the music after two hours of mouth harmonica. I tried, Toots is worth it. Judge for yourself. Its nice I think......... Enjoy
